data.description: Just listed & you don't want to miss this! Adorable 3 bed 2 bath ranch home in private neighborhood just minutes from Covington Square. Covered back patio that overlooks beautiful leveled back yard with large shed that is insulated and has electricity. Perfect yard to watch wild life from your back porch. New windows throughout entire house (August 2022), New heat pump & Air Handler (July 2022), & new toilets in master and guest bath (October 2023).
